text: Dušek (feminine Dušková) is a Czech surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Anna Dušková, Czech figure skater * Antonín Dušek, Czech ice hockey player * František Xaver Dušek, Czech composer * Jaroslav Dušek, Czech actor * Marie Dušková, Czech poet * Robert Dušek, Czech politician ==See also== * 14054 Dušek, main belt asteroid * Dusík for the Czech surname Dusík and its variant Dussek Category:Czech-language surnames
